### Phase 5: gRPC 인터페이스 및 GraphQL API 노출 (1주)

**영향 모듈:** `protobuf/`, `graphql/`, `notification/`

#### Proto 정의

```protobuf
// protobuf/src/main/proto/notification.proto

syntax = "proto3";
package com.maum.notification;

service NotificationService {
  rpc SendNotification(SendNotificationRequest) returns (SendNotificationResponse);
  rpc RegisterDeviceToken(RegisterDeviceTokenRequest) returns (RegisterDeviceTokenResponse);
  rpc UpdateNotificationSetting(UpdateNotificationSettingRequest) returns (UpdateNotificationSettingResponse);
}

message SendNotificationRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  string type    = 2; // CALL_REQUEST, MATCH, LIKE, MESSAGE, SYSTEM
  string title   = 3;
  string body    = 4;
  map<string, string> data = 5;
}

message RegisterDeviceTokenRequest {
  string user_id  = 1;
  string token    = 2;
  int32  platform = 3; // 1=iOS, 2=Android
}
```

#### GraphQL 스키마

```graphql
# graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/notification.graphqls

type NotificationSetting {
  callEnabled:    Boolean!
  matchEnabled:   Boolean!
  messageEnabled: Boolean!
}

type NotificationHistory {
  id:        ID!
  type:      String!
  title:     String!
  body:      String!
  status:    String!
  createdAt: String!
}

type Mutation {
  registerDeviceToken(token: String!, platform: Int!): Boolean!
  updateNotificationSetting(input: NotificationSettingInput!): NotificationSetting!
}

type Query {
  notificationHistory(limit: Int, lastKey: String): [NotificationHistory!]!
  notificationSetting: NotificationSetting!
}
```

